casebody.data:
OWNER-OPERATOR INDEPENDENT DRIVERS ASSOCIATION, INC., petitioner,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION, et al. No. 13-532. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
